{"tid":1457520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方指未能確定尖沙咀有女子眼部受傷與警方執法有關.    如果女事主願意提供資料，警方會樂意跟進。","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:40:48.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9afc57406fcd13cd9f01dfe77ca8601fc32232e3","tid":1457520,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474210-20190812.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474210-20190812.htm&d=5%2F0N1eX%2FnGDFGLWAFE16zqCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=35c6055c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474210-20190812.htm&h=d1e31af5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474210-20190812.htm</a><br />\n警方昨日在尖沙咀警署外進行驅散行動，期間一名女子懷疑被警方的布袋彈射中眼部，傷勢嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n警務處助理處長麥展豪表示，留意到該名女子受傷的消息，但翻看當時的電視直播片段、警員覆述的情況，以及在社交媒體的不同相片，未能確定該名女子究竟因為甚麼眼部受傷。<br />\n<br />\n他說，有相片顯示在受傷女子的眼罩旁有狀似布袋彈的物品，但亦有片段顯示沒有，警方需時理解相片的真實性，暫未能掌握足夠資料，警方會繼續搜集相關資料，如果女事主願意提供資料，警方會樂意跟進。"},{"pid":"4e0a2040620a2001e7c3dd79e0b1f88dcfcb8ce1","tid":1457520,"uid":74155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd0993b9b6eea200c4331a9802005ae33818417e","tid":1457520,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac3efce12d41f0828904beedd3c3e702bd03d60","tid":1457520,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑暗醜惡....</span></span>"},{"pid":"bc9adc97a7681f05f2c8aca691289fff6e7b9e95","tid":1457520,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco